snippet.textDisplay:
While you are watching this video, you must be thinking that you are not worthy compared to this. But God showed me many problems in this world is because of our sins. Even though you can look good outside, it does not matter with your eternity. You can still go to hell after you enjoy life on this earth. So many people are dying and going to hell because they have lost their way of direction.
We are all sinners. We know that we are bad people. Look how we hate other people, jealous, gossips, hatred toward parents, divorce, sexual sins all things. We all deserve to go to hell.
But God gave us a way out. It is really time to repent and turn to God. Believe in Jesus. He is our hope and savior of this world. He is the reason why we live. He is the one who made us and who can save us.
Turn away from this world and come to Jesus. I didn't believe in Jesus. I was always partying and clubbing, drinking, watching porn and thought life was all about money.
I was living a hopeless life even though I did not know. I was a slave to money and fame.
Then three years ago, I sought God. And God always makes Him known to those who are desperately seeking Him. The presence of God came over me and I knew I was going to hell and I knew that Jesus was the Lord and savior. His being was just so powerful that I knew He had the authority over everything.
Jesus has authority over our souls and He is calling us to repent.

Believe in Him and you will be saved. There is heaven and the door to heaven is Jesus.
When you truly surrender your life to Jesus, Holy Spirit will come to you and change and transform you.
All my addictions disappeared supernaturally just in one day when I gave my life to Christ.
He loves our young generation who has been lost so so so much because He knows how we are so unloving and how deceived we are. But now it's time. Come to Jesus, believe in Jesus! He is a good good shepherd who will give you living water.
